    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/393380/extras/140879fff09516d9a6c1abaf57152f1c.avif?t=1771613283\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/393380/extras_big/140879fff09516d9a6c1abaf57152f1c.avif?t=1771613283 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >小队步兵战斗的新改进！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们对战术小队的步兵作战进行了全面改革，以创造尽可能有趣、身临其境和真实的步兵作战体验。这是为了更加强调小队团队合作和战术的核心原则。和你的小队一起战斗，压制敌人，从胜利走向胜利！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >船新版本的压制效果！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以全新的压制效果放下火力，旨在帮助玩家在任何交火中更灵活地攻击和防御。有效使用它可以掩护你的小队，遮蔽敌人的视线，更多的降低敌方压制火力的瞄准能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >逼真的镜中视野！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;战术小队现在拥有比以往任何时候都更逼真的全新瞄准镜视角。现在，当你透过你最喜欢的瞄准镜瞄准目标时，你会看到你的目标更真实的景象，就像真正的狙击手那样。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/393380/extras/9ae95ce43ddaf97a8ea4dd4665c47b73.avif?t=1771613283\" width=600 height=150 /></span>战术小队是一款大型联合兵种多人第一人称射击游戏，通过沟通、团队游戏和强大的团队凝聚力来强调战斗真实性，并融入更大规模的协调、战术和计划中。广泛选择的现实派系特定武器和车辆允许玩家建立自己的装载，最适合他们喜欢的战术。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战术小队拥有13个派系、25张大型地图、基于车辆的不同组合，玩法和玩家构建的基地，在现实世界规模的交火中，通过瞬间的决策，创造了一种令人心跳加速、直击内心的游戏体验。&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/393380/extras/b15a7140df51da5333186e84af6a091d.poster.avif?t=1771613283\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/393380/extras/b15a7140df51da5333186e84af6a091d.webm?t=1771613283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/393380/extras/b15a7140df51da5333186e84af6a091d.mp4?t=1771613283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >50 对 50</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战术小队旨在创造真实的战斗体验，同时让传统和非传统派系相互对抗。作为50人团队的一员，加入一个9人小队，在大型现实世界环境中与对方50人团队进行激烈的战斗。该小队由美国陆军、海军陆战队、俄罗斯地面部队、英国陆军、加拿大武装部队、澳大利亚陆军、中东联盟、非正规民兵和叛乱分子组成，每个阵营都有自己独特的武器库。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/393380/extras/4fe8b2cae3d3db0eb860e8629280306a.poster.avif?t=1771613283\" width=450 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/393380/extras/4fe8b2cae3d3db0eb860e8629280306a.webm?t=1771613283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/393380/extras/4fe8b2cae3d3db0eb860e8629280306a.mp4?t=1771613283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建筑系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过建造防御工事和阵地来适应战场不断变化的需求，为您的小队和团队提供优势。无论是放置重机枪和反坦克炮阵地，还是用沙袋、防爆块和铁丝网加固阵地，只要你有足够的材料，战场都可以变成你的形状。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/393380/extras/25eefc413b61345cdc24f5f49c202a52.poster.avif?t=1771613283\" width=450 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/393380/extras/25eefc413b61345cdc24f5f49c202a52.webm?t=1771613283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/393380/extras/25eefc413b61345cdc24f5f49c202a52.mp4?t=1771613283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >通信</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沟通是士兵有效与敌人交战的最佳工具。为了有助于在战场上驾驭复杂的通信，战术小队提供了一个顶级的游戏内语音沟通系统，玩家可以在本地、班内、班组长之间或班组长与团队指挥官交谈。地图工具和世界标记有助于指挥官和队长向他们的小队通报交战的战术。</p>",
